WEBVTT

01:37.950 --> 01:40.550
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.410 --> 01:43.570
[Episode 11]

01:47.430 --> 01:49.160
What happened to Immortal Xin?

01:51.430 --> 01:53.000
Her body can't retain water.

01:53.000 --> 01:54.229
The Fish Drinking Technique

01:54.229 --> 01:56.070
won't be effective for her for too long.

01:56.070 --> 01:57.330
Is there any other way?

01:58.840 --> 02:00.760
The only way
to break the Spell of Utterance

02:00.760 --> 02:02.560
is to kill the person who cast it.

02:03.000 --> 02:04.000
Then go kill them.

02:04.150 --> 02:05.280
You are good at this.

02:06.000 --> 02:07.460
She's being targeted now.

02:07.680 --> 02:08.470
If I leave,

02:08.470 --> 02:09.669
who will protect her?

02:11.220 --> 02:12.430
It's not like you're the only one alive

02:12.430 --> 02:13.630
in Chongling valley.

02:20.000 --> 02:20.710
Miss, can you see

02:20.710 --> 02:22.510
the golden lotus on my forehead?

02:22.960 --> 02:23.680
I can.

02:24.190 --> 02:24.990
What about it?

02:25.079 --> 02:26.410
Since the day I was born,

02:27.079 --> 02:28.079
this golden lotus

02:28.520 --> 02:29.710
has grown with me.

02:33.870 --> 02:35.930
I was born
on the 9th day of September.

02:36.500 --> 02:37.430
Logically,

02:37.910 --> 02:39.570
September is already autumn,

02:39.960 --> 02:40.630
but the lotus

02:40.630 --> 02:41.829
in the pond at my house

02:42.030 --> 02:43.090
had never bloomed.

02:44.280 --> 02:46.480
They all said it was an auspicious sign.

02:47.010 --> 02:47.710
Sure enough.

02:47.710 --> 02:48.280
Master!

02:48.870 --> 02:50.070
On the day of my birth,

02:50.280 --> 02:51.840
anomalies appeared in the sky,

02:51.840 --> 02:54.040
and rainbow light stretched for miles.

03:08.750 --> 03:09.190
Fun!

03:09.470 --> 03:10.520
When I was four,

03:10.910 --> 03:12.520
people from Tianyin Mountain came,

03:12.520 --> 03:13.960
saying I had natural immortal perception

03:13.960 --> 03:15.820
and a destiny with the immortals.

03:15.910 --> 03:18.770
They wanted to take me up the mountain
to cultivate.

03:19.520 --> 03:20.430
Young man.

03:21.150 --> 03:23.520
I see
you have a natural immortal perception

03:23.520 --> 03:25.120
and a great destiny with the immortals.

03:25.120 --> 03:27.470
Would you like to
come up the mountain with me to cultivate?

03:25.200 --> 03:27.170
[Tianyin Mountain Sect Master]

03:31.240 --> 03:32.030
Never mind.

03:32.560 --> 03:35.079
You have not yet
severed your ties to the mortal world.

03:35.079 --> 03:36.240
In 20 years,

03:36.590 --> 03:38.390
when you have severed your ties,

03:39.079 --> 03:42.079
come to Tianyin Mountain to find me.

03:46.400 --> 03:48.840
The golden lotus
in the pond has its own cultivation method

03:48.840 --> 03:50.800
and now recognizes me as its master.

03:50.800 --> 03:52.060
Though I am but a child,

03:52.240 --> 03:54.430
I have already stepped
onto the path of cultivation.

03:54.430 --> 03:55.160
Sure enough.

03:55.800 --> 03:56.930
Twenty years later,

03:57.430 --> 03:59.400
my parents passed away one after another.

03:59.400 --> 04:00.800
I had no more attachments

04:01.280 --> 04:02.410
in the mortal world.

04:04.190 --> 04:05.000
-Jin Lun!
-Jin Lun!

04:05.000 --> 04:05.800
Where are you going?

04:05.800 --> 04:06.910
Jin Lun, where are you going?

04:06.910 --> 04:07.640
At that time,

04:08.240 --> 04:11.900
I had already cultivated to
the Foundation Establishment Stage.

04:24.270 --> 04:25.630
I worked hard cultivating along the way,

04:25.630 --> 04:26.760
walking for 3 years,

04:27.240 --> 04:29.570
and finally arrived at Tianyin Mountain.

04:30.000 --> 04:31.730
But at the foot of the mountain,

04:32.000 --> 04:32.920
I saw someone.

04:37.510 --> 04:38.370
Leave quickly.

04:38.560 --> 04:39.920
The masters of Tianyin Mountain

04:39.920 --> 04:42.000
only come down the mountain
once every 3 to 5 years.

04:42.000 --> 04:43.159
Begging for food here,

04:43.159 --> 04:44.560
you will starve to death.

05:06.990 --> 05:08.190
Your face is injured.

05:08.600 --> 05:09.800
Bandage it with that.

05:35.560 --> 05:38.000
I sat at the foot of the mountain
for 3 months,

05:38.000 --> 05:39.240
but I couldn't get up

05:39.830 --> 05:41.870
and take a single step
onto the stone stairs.

05:41.870 --> 05:43.000
Three months later,

05:43.240 --> 05:44.830
Master came down the mountain

05:44.830 --> 05:46.760
and asked if I still wanted to go up.

05:54.680 --> 05:56.810
Do you still want to go up the mountain?

05:57.270 --> 05:57.830
Yes.

05:58.510 --> 06:00.070
Then why don't you go?

06:05.560 --> 06:06.290
I don't know.

06:12.800 --> 06:13.680
Does it hurt?

06:14.240 --> 06:14.800
Yes.

06:15.040 --> 06:16.300
Is your mind clear now?

06:17.270 --> 06:18.510
Do you know why now?

06:21.720 --> 06:23.000
Since you don't know,

06:23.240 --> 06:25.500
then go into the world and think about it.

06:25.830 --> 06:28.600
If you figure it out after 10 years,

06:29.830 --> 06:31.190
come back to look for me.

06:36.950 --> 06:38.750
This year makes it the 10th year.

06:39.040 --> 06:39.920
We meet again.

06:41.310 --> 06:42.040
So?

06:45.190 --> 06:45.920
I don't know.

06:46.870 --> 06:47.730
You don't know?

06:51.680 --> 06:53.800
I was enlightened
by my master since childhood.

06:53.800 --> 06:55.400
My mind is calm as a millpond—

06:55.610 --> 06:56.870
without joy or sorrow.

06:57.040 --> 06:58.920
There is nothing in this world

06:58.920 --> 07:00.270
that can stir my heart.

07:00.900 --> 07:02.630
But ever since the day I met you,

07:05.070 --> 07:05.800
my heart

07:06.560 --> 07:08.020
has never been calm again.

07:10.830 --> 07:11.890
I once asked others

07:12.830 --> 07:14.030
what this feeling is.

07:14.680 --> 07:15.600
They told me

07:16.310 --> 07:17.640
it's called affection.

07:18.750 --> 07:19.880
I don't understand.

07:21.190 --> 07:22.160
To me,

07:22.720 --> 07:24.580
I think you are more like a riddle.

07:25.270 --> 07:26.720
But right at this moment,

07:27.240 --> 07:28.560
with you so close to me,

07:29.630 --> 07:30.480
I seem to

07:31.270 --> 07:33.600
have a trace of understanding in my heart.

07:35.190 --> 07:36.850
Making my Dao heart unsteady,

07:37.800 --> 07:39.400
you might be my tribulation.

07:40.040 --> 07:41.830
Perhaps if I just keep following you,

07:41.830 --> 07:43.159
I can solve this riddle.

07:47.720 --> 07:49.120
I don't think you have the chance

07:49.120 --> 07:49.860
to solve it.

07:56.870 --> 07:58.270
Power-Dissolving Powder?

07:58.270 --> 07:59.270
It's a nice story,

07:59.720 --> 08:00.780
but I don't like it.

08:11.040 --> 08:12.270
I've long heard that Tianyin Mountain's

08:12.270 --> 08:13.360
Golden Bracelet of Demon Suppression

08:13.360 --> 08:15.160
is a top-tier magical artifact.

08:15.600 --> 08:17.400
I didn't expect it to be with you.

08:19.240 --> 08:21.240
Since you have heard of this treasure,

08:21.240 --> 08:22.100
you should know

08:23.240 --> 08:24.680
that the bracelet recognizes its master

08:24.680 --> 08:26.480
and is long connected to my mind.

08:26.830 --> 08:28.430
If I don't want to take it off,

08:28.570 --> 08:29.810
no one can take it,

08:30.630 --> 08:31.830
nor can they touch me.

08:32.630 --> 08:34.030
Don't follow me anymore.

08:34.240 --> 08:35.500
If there is a next time,

08:35.600 --> 08:38.460
even Tianyin Mountain
won't be able to protect you.

09:00.270 --> 09:00.960
Mr. Lu.

09:02.480 --> 09:03.810
I brought you some food.

09:04.790 --> 09:05.650
Please come in.

09:14.960 --> 09:15.960
Is this all for me?

09:17.270 --> 09:17.790
Yes.

09:18.750 --> 09:19.910
But there's so much.

09:20.030 --> 09:21.030
I can't eat it all.

09:23.000 --> 09:24.150
I have some business recently

09:24.150 --> 09:25.320
and need to leave the valley for a while.

09:25.320 --> 09:27.390
I won't be able to
come take care of you often.

09:27.390 --> 09:28.190
After I leave,

09:28.440 --> 09:30.030
you must practice
the Fish Drinking Technique frequently.

09:30.030 --> 09:30.960
Don't slack off.

09:31.840 --> 09:32.510
I will.

09:35.960 --> 09:36.600
Mr. Lu.

09:40.150 --> 09:41.550
Is what you're going to do

09:41.670 --> 09:42.480
dangerous?

09:43.840 --> 09:44.510
No.

09:46.440 --> 09:47.240
Then I hope

09:47.670 --> 09:48.910
everything goes smoothly,

09:48.910 --> 09:50.170
and you return safely.

09:51.150 --> 09:51.720
Okay.

10:17.080 --> 10:17.740
Senior Bai,

10:18.630 --> 10:19.560
that night, I saw

10:19.870 --> 10:20.630
Junior Jiang wound

10:20.630 --> 10:22.440
that male cultivator with her sword.

10:22.440 --> 10:23.840
But in the blink of an eye,

10:23.960 --> 10:25.670
his wound healed completely.

10:26.270 --> 10:28.120
Don't you find that a bit strange?

10:28.120 --> 10:29.200
But Junior Jiang's Chengying Sword

10:29.200 --> 10:30.360
is no ordinary weapon.

10:30.360 --> 10:31.670
Even a Nascent Soul cultivator

10:31.670 --> 10:32.600
won't be able to recover

10:32.600 --> 10:33.510
that quickly after being injured

10:33.510 --> 10:34.550
by it.

10:49.870 --> 10:51.000
War Demon.

10:52.270 --> 10:53.200
Could it be him?

10:56.550 --> 10:57.950
Why did you come to see me?

11:02.790 --> 11:04.650
I was worried about your illness.

11:05.390 --> 11:06.720
Are you feeling better?

11:06.790 --> 11:08.000
It's not completely cured yet,

11:08.000 --> 11:09.630
but I found a way to relieve it,

11:09.630 --> 11:10.830
so it's not terrible.

11:12.150 --> 11:12.870
And you?

11:14.480 --> 11:15.410
I'm much better.

11:16.000 --> 11:17.870
Mr. Li took me to see a doctor.

11:20.840 --> 11:23.330
How many years did Li Si serve

11:23.480 --> 11:24.550
under your father?

11:28.720 --> 11:29.670
Three years.

11:31.790 --> 11:33.190
Have you seen him before?

11:35.240 --> 11:36.320
I mean,

11:36.550 --> 11:38.000
did you know him

11:38.270 --> 11:40.070
before your father passed away?

11:42.150 --> 11:43.030
So,

11:43.510 --> 11:45.040
you didn't know him before.

11:53.080 --> 11:54.600
What's wrong?

11:55.910 --> 11:56.630
Nothing.

11:56.910 --> 11:57.840
I'm just asking.

11:59.030 --> 12:00.690
Thank you for coming to see me.

12:07.070 --> 12:13.100
[Pingxiang Town]

12:14.630 --> 12:16.360
This place is neither big

12:16.440 --> 12:17.200
nor small,

12:17.790 --> 12:18.960
but finding someone

12:19.200 --> 12:20.360
is not that easy.

12:21.790 --> 12:23.250
How about asking someone?

12:23.790 --> 12:25.150
If you put it that way,

12:26.030 --> 12:28.630
it should be in Pingxiang Town.

12:29.270 --> 12:30.280
I was traveling,

12:30.790 --> 12:32.270
and then I met a

12:32.270 --> 12:33.440
crazy man

12:33.720 --> 12:34.780
running toward me.

12:35.340 --> 12:36.510
Looking at his appearance,

12:36.510 --> 12:37.790
he didn't look like someone
from the Central Plains.

12:37.790 --> 12:39.920
He looked like he was from North Xiang.

12:40.790 --> 12:42.150
Even people from North Xiang are coming

12:42.150 --> 12:42.870
to beg here.

12:43.550 --> 12:44.390
It's strange.

12:44.480 --> 12:45.750
What do you think they're after?

12:45.750 --> 12:47.720
That guy is a fool.

12:48.750 --> 12:50.410
God knows what he's thinking.

12:50.600 --> 12:51.130
Exactly.

12:51.720 --> 12:52.790
We found him.

12:53.150 --> 12:53.950
You're lucky.

12:54.390 --> 12:55.150
Sirs!

12:56.030 --> 12:56.830
Wait a minute!

12:57.440 --> 12:58.200
What is it?

12:58.670 --> 13:00.390
The man from North Xiang you just mentioned—

13:00.390 --> 13:01.050
where is he?

13:01.870 --> 13:03.000
We see him every day.

13:03.600 --> 13:05.330
He's right in that shack ahead.

13:05.870 --> 13:06.270
But

13:06.440 --> 13:07.840
why are you looking for him?

13:07.840 --> 13:09.370
That fool can't even speak.

13:09.510 --> 13:11.320
He's starving so badly
he eats everything.

13:11.320 --> 13:13.050
And he lies down when he's full.

13:16.000 --> 13:16.600
Thank you.

13:17.900 --> 13:18.320
Thank you.

13:18.320 --> 13:19.180
Thank you, Sir.

13:19.510 --> 13:20.440
You're welcome.

13:21.360 --> 13:22.820
-We're rich!
-We're rich!

13:26.600 --> 13:27.200
Sirs,

13:27.440 --> 13:28.870
is there anyone from North Xiang here?

13:28.870 --> 13:30.150
North Xiang?

13:30.150 --> 13:30.990
Over there.

13:31.080 --> 13:31.960
Next door.

13:32.800 --> 13:33.520
Thank you.

13:33.550 --> 13:34.240
Thank you.

13:34.360 --> 13:35.150
Thank you.

13:40.080 --> 13:41.540
He's in a pretty bad state.

13:53.750 --> 13:54.750
Spare me, My Lord!

13:54.840 --> 13:55.840
Spare me, My Lord!

13:55.840 --> 13:56.630
Don't kill me!

13:56.630 --> 13:58.240
Don't kill me! Don't kill me!

13:59.550 --> 14:00.480
I won't kill you.

14:01.360 --> 14:03.160
I just want to ask you a question.

14:04.240 --> 14:06.300
Who asked you to pass on that message?

14:09.170 --> 14:10.050
Your hands

14:10.270 --> 14:12.670
don't look like they practice
with a blade.

14:13.440 --> 14:14.900
I am good at short weapons,

14:14.960 --> 14:16.620
and occasionally use swords.

14:16.620 --> 14:17.910
I used to be a scout,

14:18.270 --> 14:20.030
focusing mainly on reconnaissance.

14:20.030 --> 14:21.720
If I ever have to fight enemies in battle,

14:21.720 --> 14:22.510
it's probably because I'm exposed

14:22.510 --> 14:23.630
or surrounded.

14:24.270 --> 14:25.790
When it's really time to fight
for my life,

14:25.790 --> 14:28.190
it doesn't matter
if I use a blade or a sword.

14:28.870 --> 14:30.240
Rest early, Miss Xin.

14:30.600 --> 14:31.200
Farewell.

14:33.120 --> 14:35.520
His injuries were clearly caused by magic.

14:35.960 --> 14:36.910
Why did he lie?

14:38.140 --> 14:40.940
What is his purpose
in coming to Chongling Valley?

14:47.480 --> 14:48.240
Find Li Si.

15:53.240 --> 15:54.000
Found him.

16:17.480 --> 16:18.600
Judging by his figure,

16:18.600 --> 16:19.200
he seems to be the one

16:19.200 --> 16:20.600
who fought us that night.

16:21.270 --> 16:22.670
I have my suspicions too.

16:22.870 --> 16:24.870
But this person carries
the Gongshan Jade Tablet.

16:24.870 --> 16:26.360
No matter if it's him or not,

16:26.360 --> 16:27.690
let's follow him first.

16:28.200 --> 16:29.120
Young Sect Master,

16:29.120 --> 16:30.920
why don't we use magic to travel?

16:31.830 --> 16:33.270
I've scouted around the past 2 days.

16:33.270 --> 16:35.440
There are formations everywhere
in Chongling Valley.

16:35.440 --> 16:36.840
Let alone using magic to travel,

16:36.840 --> 16:38.300
even if we run a bit faster,

16:38.360 --> 16:40.020
we might trigger a formation.

16:41.510 --> 16:42.310
What's wrong?

16:43.200 --> 16:46.030
He is using glutinous rice flour
to test the formations.

16:46.030 --> 16:48.760
Could he be trying to
steal the Immortality Pill?

16:50.010 --> 16:50.770
I don't know.

16:52.670 --> 16:53.200
Let's go.

16:53.960 --> 16:54.490
This way.

17:53.070 --> 17:55.480
The connection
to the paper figure is broken.

17:55.480 --> 17:56.350
He found out.

18:00.680 --> 18:01.400
Oh no.

18:13.310 --> 18:14.510
What happened to him?

18:14.510 --> 18:15.680
We don't know either.

18:15.680 --> 18:16.790
When we were passing by,

18:16.790 --> 18:17.990
we heard some noises,

18:18.400 --> 18:19.310
so we came in.

18:19.830 --> 18:20.830
Is he still alive?

18:22.680 --> 18:23.270
Yes.

18:30.580 --> 18:33.090
[Filled with Vitality and Grace]

18:42.160 --> 18:42.720
Doctor,

18:43.200 --> 18:44.640
how is Mr. Li?

18:47.310 --> 18:48.110
He's fine.

18:48.640 --> 18:50.640
It's just some superficial wounds.

18:50.640 --> 18:51.880
He'll wake up soon.

19:08.160 --> 19:09.290
Why are you all here?

19:09.960 --> 19:10.820
What happened?

19:17.160 --> 19:17.680
Oh no.

19:18.270 --> 19:18.920
It's gone.

19:19.310 --> 19:20.040
What's gone?

19:21.680 --> 19:22.790
The Gongshan Jade Tablet.

19:22.790 --> 19:23.390
It's gone?

19:23.680 --> 19:25.160
I saw a dark figure earlier.

19:25.160 --> 19:27.030
I thought it looked suspicious,
so I followed it.

19:27.030 --> 19:28.200
I was ambushed by that person

19:28.200 --> 19:29.330
and was knocked out.

19:29.680 --> 19:30.480
When I woke up,

19:32.240 --> 19:33.940
the Gongshan Jade Tablet was gone.

19:33.940 --> 19:35.440
When you were fighting him,

19:35.440 --> 19:36.570
did you see his face?

19:36.850 --> 19:38.000
Was there anything notable?

19:38.000 --> 19:38.860
It was too dark.

19:39.240 --> 19:39.880
He was masked.

19:39.880 --> 19:41.160
I couldn't see clearly.

19:41.160 --> 19:42.220
I only remember...

19:43.590 --> 19:44.920
he had a sharp gaze.

19:45.720 --> 19:46.480
His moves

19:47.160 --> 19:48.490
were also very vicious.

20:05.110 --> 20:05.790
Li Si?

21:13.830 --> 21:14.760
It really is you.

21:33.580 --> 21:34.100
Look,

21:34.620 --> 21:36.030
Xutuo City is right ahead.

21:36.030 --> 21:36.750
I met him there

21:36.750 --> 21:37.680
when I was moving

21:37.790 --> 21:38.440
the goods.

21:45.400 --> 21:46.350
Take a look, Sir.

21:46.640 --> 21:48.240
Top-quality leather drums.

21:55.070 --> 21:55.790
I saw him

21:55.790 --> 21:56.720
right around here.

21:56.720 --> 21:57.520
When I saw him,

21:57.920 --> 21:58.680
he was wearing

21:58.680 --> 22:00.030
fine silk from the Central Plains.

22:00.030 --> 22:01.350
It looked very expensive

22:01.350 --> 22:02.480
and finely crafted.

22:19.810 --> 22:21.740
Are they clothes of that material?

22:22.480 --> 22:23.200
Yes.

22:41.930 --> 22:43.330
Don't waste your energy.

22:45.030 --> 22:45.830
It's useless.

22:46.350 --> 22:47.880
I didn't want to target you.

22:48.160 --> 22:49.030
But since you found out,

22:49.030 --> 22:49.890
I had no choice.

22:50.780 --> 22:52.440
I have important things to do.

22:52.440 --> 22:53.700
I can't let you ruin it.

22:58.160 --> 22:59.760
Just bear with it here
for a couple of days.

22:59.760 --> 23:00.550
Once I'm done,

23:00.550 --> 23:02.810
someone will naturally come to save you.

23:03.720 --> 23:04.310
Miss Xin.

23:05.240 --> 23:06.440
You are a good person.

23:06.500 --> 23:08.000
I don't want to make things difficult
for you.

23:08.000 --> 23:09.110
But I also beg you—

23:10.000 --> 23:12.000
don't make things difficult for me.

23:34.110 --> 23:34.970
I remember now.

23:35.480 --> 23:36.750
I was near here when I saw

23:36.750 --> 23:37.750
that person then.

23:38.640 --> 23:40.920
So he's from the Qinghong Sect.

23:42.000 --> 23:43.460
What is the Qinghong Sect?

23:43.750 --> 23:44.880
The Qinghong Sect in North Xiang

23:44.880 --> 23:46.440
is known to be somewhere glorious.

23:46.440 --> 23:47.650
It has been passed down
for a thousand years.

23:47.650 --> 23:49.200
Legend has it that the Grandmaster

23:49.200 --> 23:51.160
is the Phoenix God from the divine realm.

23:51.160 --> 23:52.590
He descended to the mortal world

23:52.590 --> 23:53.750
to help people achieve enlightenment,

23:53.750 --> 23:54.750
relieve disasters,

23:54.750 --> 23:56.010
and spread blessings.

23:57.260 --> 23:58.720
How many of them are there?

23:58.790 --> 23:59.890
They are many.

24:00.400 --> 24:01.070
Besides the Grandmaster

24:01.070 --> 24:02.440
and his Left and Right Guardians,

24:02.440 --> 24:03.440
the Four Dharma Kings,

24:03.440 --> 24:04.440
the Eight Vajras,

24:04.480 --> 24:06.410
and the Sixteen Branch Masters...

24:06.720 --> 24:08.350
If you add the Fire Guards,

24:08.640 --> 24:09.640
there are at least

24:09.800 --> 24:11.410
tens of thousands of them.

24:12.000 --> 24:13.060
This Qinghong Sect

24:13.270 --> 24:14.400
is the state religion.

24:14.400 --> 24:15.800
Even our North Xiang King

24:16.030 --> 24:17.510
is their devout follower.

24:17.920 --> 24:19.130
How can such a small place

24:19.130 --> 24:20.500
hold so many people?

24:22.130 --> 24:23.640
This isn't their headquarters, is it?

24:23.640 --> 24:24.240
Right.

24:24.920 --> 24:26.000
This is the Qinghong Sect's

24:26.000 --> 24:27.240
Bishui Branch.

24:27.680 --> 24:30.080
I heard the Branch Master
is called Hewabu.

24:30.480 --> 24:32.350
He and Dharma King Wen Yin
are cousins.

24:32.350 --> 24:33.010
Therefore,

24:33.200 --> 24:35.350
he holds a prominent position in the sect.

24:35.350 --> 24:36.070
Not only has he mastered

24:36.070 --> 24:37.510
the Indestructible Vajra Divine Physique,

24:37.510 --> 24:38.200
but he has also learned

24:38.200 --> 24:39.800
the magic of Divine Command.

24:40.440 --> 24:41.920
Although the number of people
in this branch

24:41.920 --> 24:43.030
cannot compare to the headquarters,

24:43.030 --> 24:44.750
there are still

24:45.200 --> 24:46.260
thousands of them.

24:47.030 --> 24:48.430
How many doors are there?

24:49.510 --> 24:50.160
One.

24:52.000 --> 24:53.240
That's good.

24:53.920 --> 24:54.510
Huh?

24:55.160 --> 24:56.440
What are you going to do?

24:56.440 --> 24:56.970
Don't...

24:57.240 --> 24:58.420
Don't provoke them.

24:58.920 --> 24:59.750
They have received

24:59.750 --> 25:01.150
blessings from the gods.

25:01.170 --> 25:02.040
Even 10 personal guards

25:02.040 --> 25:03.070
under North Xiang King

25:03.070 --> 25:04.330
can't beat one of them.

25:04.640 --> 25:05.700
If you offend them,

25:06.030 --> 25:07.000
you're dead.

25:07.440 --> 25:09.570
This is none of your business anymore.

25:12.350 --> 25:13.680
Why aren't you leaving?

25:37.750 --> 25:38.830
If you want to get out,

25:38.830 --> 25:40.560
you have to do something for me.

25:45.310 --> 25:46.240
Where did you hide

25:46.240 --> 25:47.240
your Gongshan Jade Tablet?

25:47.240 --> 25:48.240
Give me the jade tablet,

25:48.240 --> 25:49.970
and I'll save you immediately.

25:50.200 --> 25:52.130
So it was you who broke into my room.

25:53.070 --> 25:53.730
Who are you?

25:53.990 --> 25:55.450
It doesn't matter who I am.

25:55.480 --> 25:56.270
What matters is that

25:56.270 --> 25:58.030
only I can save you now.

25:58.640 --> 26:00.830
Where is the Gongshan Jade Tablet hidden?

26:00.830 --> 26:01.640
Save me,

26:02.030 --> 26:03.160
and I'll take you to find it.

26:03.160 --> 26:04.980
Stop talking nonsense.
Are you going to tell me or not?

26:04.980 --> 26:05.880
If you don't take me out,

26:05.880 --> 26:06.810
how can I find it?

26:07.010 --> 26:07.960
You won't tell me?

26:07.960 --> 26:08.510
Fine.

26:09.590 --> 26:10.850
Then I have my own ways.

26:16.830 --> 26:18.240
The Soul Search Technique.

26:18.240 --> 26:19.030
I didn't want

26:19.030 --> 26:20.360
to torture you this way,

26:20.510 --> 26:22.400
but unfortunately, you're too stubborn.

26:22.400 --> 26:24.200
I'll just have to find it myself.

26:33.070 --> 26:33.920
You from the Central Plains,

26:33.920 --> 26:35.720
this is not a place you should be.

26:42.480 --> 26:43.410
Wait for me here.

26:44.110 --> 26:44.920
I thought so.

26:44.950 --> 26:47.130
[Bishui Branch]

27:22.310 --> 27:23.480
Immortal sect dog,

27:24.070 --> 27:26.000
the fact that you made it to me alive

27:26.400 --> 27:28.010
shows you have some skills,

27:28.480 --> 27:29.140
and that

27:29.640 --> 27:31.590
I raised a bunch of useless trash.

27:43.640 --> 27:44.550
Do you know

27:44.920 --> 27:46.240
you ruined my dinner?

27:46.510 --> 27:47.330
What you're going to lose

27:47.330 --> 27:48.850
isn't just your dinner,

27:49.070 --> 27:50.130
but also your life.

27:52.550 --> 27:53.880
Why did you kill Xin Mei?

27:59.480 --> 28:00.270
Are you talking about that

28:00.270 --> 28:01.530
Central Plains woman?

28:01.960 --> 28:02.680
Is she dead?

28:03.440 --> 28:04.570
Why did you kill her?

28:05.590 --> 28:06.640
Why?

28:08.750 --> 28:10.280
Because she killed Mr. Gui.

28:11.240 --> 28:12.110
And you,

28:12.400 --> 28:13.830
since you slaughtered so many followers

28:13.830 --> 28:15.030
of my Phoenix God today,

28:15.030 --> 28:16.680
go down and keep her company,

28:17.240 --> 28:18.310
and face the Phoenix God's

28:18.310 --> 28:19.920
punishment together.

29:47.480 --> 29:47.880
Who...

29:48.510 --> 29:49.830
Who are you?

29:50.400 --> 29:51.860
One who's after your life.

29:52.880 --> 29:54.750
I am the envoy of the Phoenix God.

29:56.000 --> 29:57.200
My god's glory

29:58.640 --> 30:00.170
can replace the sun and moon

30:00.750 --> 30:02.150
and shine upon the world.

30:03.880 --> 30:04.880
God.

30:05.720 --> 30:08.830
Please give me the supreme power.

30:09.270 --> 30:10.310
Through my hands,

30:12.070 --> 30:14.000
turn this blasphemer

30:14.480 --> 30:15.960
to ashes.

30:34.270 --> 30:35.870
Golden Core to Nascent Soul.

30:36.680 --> 30:37.830
Advancing right on the spot?

30:37.830 --> 30:39.160
Master is mighty!

30:39.200 --> 30:41.260
The Phoenix God's power is unmatched

30:41.270 --> 30:42.640
and invincible!

30:42.750 --> 30:44.410
Even if the Phoenix God comes,

30:44.640 --> 30:45.570
they will have to

30:45.680 --> 30:47.110
die with you today.

30:57.920 --> 30:58.640
Found it.

31:00.110 --> 31:01.710
Your jade tablet is mine now.

31:12.200 --> 31:13.240
The Golden Body!

31:20.750 --> 31:21.880
Ignorant mortal,

31:22.830 --> 31:24.920
accept the wrath of the Phoenix God!

31:27.640 --> 31:29.890
♪ I ask the Nine Heavens:
what is the purpose of this life? ♪

31:29.920 --> 31:32.710
♪ With my spine as my monument,
I shall never kneel ♪

31:33.680 --> 31:35.780
♪ Though this life be wretched,
I will not sink so low ♪

31:35.800 --> 31:38.620
♪ As to become a puppet of fate ♪

31:39.750 --> 31:42.100
♪ What is the purpose of life?
To draw my blade and slay evil ♪

31:42.130 --> 31:45.350
♪ Even if I am turned to dust,
I will not regret ♪

31:46.270 --> 31:48.270
♪ By my will,
I shall bring back the sun and moon ♪

31:48.340 --> 31:51.290
♪ And restore clear radiance
to the mortal realm ♪

31:51.930 --> 31:55.290
♪ Rather than bowing my back
to apologize to the Heavens ♪

31:55.650 --> 31:58.400
♪ I would sooner rewrite
this fated calamity ♪

31:58.590 --> 32:01.110
♪ I demand the story
follow my own desire ♪

32:01.330 --> 32:03.920
♪ To serve as its final conclusion ♪

32:46.590 --> 32:49.400
You... You will die
from a spiritual energy riot!

32:53.440 --> 32:54.270
You...

32:54.590 --> 32:56.240
You will bleed
from your seven orifices and die!

32:56.240 --> 32:57.640
You will commit suicide!

32:57.960 --> 32:59.690
You... You will die instantly!

32:59.720 --> 33:01.030
You... drop dead!

33:04.030 --> 33:04.960
What's going on?

33:05.310 --> 33:05.920
Run!

33:11.680 --> 33:14.030
It's such
a superficial Spell of Utterance—

33:14.030 --> 33:15.070
how could you show it off,

33:15.070 --> 33:16.470
embarrassing yourself.

33:16.680 --> 33:17.440
I'm curious.

33:18.000 --> 33:20.270
Spell of Utterance is a high-level spell.

33:20.270 --> 33:21.310
Even Cave Void cultivators

33:21.310 --> 33:22.640
find it hard to control.

33:22.640 --> 33:23.350
You were just

33:23.350 --> 33:24.810
a Golden Core cultivator.

33:24.880 --> 33:26.080
How did you master it?

33:28.880 --> 33:30.210
What did you just drink?

33:33.030 --> 33:34.230
Why should I tell you?

33:34.920 --> 33:35.780
The Phoenix God

33:35.960 --> 33:36.890
will punish you.

33:39.440 --> 33:41.750
You really are hell-bent on seeing
your own funeral, aren't you?

33:41.750 --> 33:42.880
Would you like to see

33:43.240 --> 33:45.700
what the real Spell of Utterance
looks like?

33:49.350 --> 33:51.680
Your hands are covered in blood,

33:51.880 --> 33:53.510
and you're burdened with sin.

33:53.510 --> 33:54.370
At this moment,

33:54.640 --> 33:56.160
you will bleed out of your seven orifices,

33:56.160 --> 33:58.290
and your meridians will be broken off.

34:16.150 --> 34:17.710
Calm your anger, God.
Calm your anger, God.

34:17.710 --> 34:18.800
We are willing to surrender

34:18.800 --> 34:19.840
and serve you!

34:20.150 --> 34:21.230
Calm your anger, God.

34:21.230 --> 34:22.630
We are willing to surrender

34:22.630 --> 34:23.630
and serve you!

34:24.000 --> 34:25.199
Calm your anger, God.

34:26.360 --> 34:27.360
In this hall,

34:28.110 --> 34:29.070
anyone who has killed

34:29.070 --> 34:30.480
innocent people

34:31.159 --> 34:32.690
will die by their own hands.

34:52.960 --> 34:53.760
It's settled?

34:54.320 --> 34:54.920
Let's go.

35:00.880 --> 35:01.510
Have a sip.

35:13.190 --> 35:14.120
I've recovered?

35:14.960 --> 35:16.290
It can absorb water now?

36:02.230 --> 36:02.880
Kill him.

36:03.150 --> 36:03.800
Wait.

36:05.880 --> 36:06.880
Divine Doctor Su,

36:07.000 --> 36:09.060
please let me ask him a few questions.

36:17.960 --> 36:18.590
When did

36:18.590 --> 36:19.760
your plan start?

36:20.510 --> 36:22.360
Was it after entering Chongling Valley,

36:22.360 --> 36:24.160
when we met in the ruined temple,

36:24.440 --> 36:25.370
or even earlier?

36:26.110 --> 36:28.310
I don't understand what you're saying.

36:28.440 --> 36:29.630
You broke
the mountain protection formation,

36:29.630 --> 36:30.800
sneaked outside the Jiujue Cave,

36:30.800 --> 36:32.840
and almost destroyed
the Dragon-Severing Stone.

36:32.840 --> 36:33.360
I see you've put

36:33.360 --> 36:34.360
a lot of thought

36:34.360 --> 36:36.150
into every step you took to get here.

36:36.150 --> 36:37.800
If you want to steal the Immortality Pill,
just say it.

36:37.800 --> 36:38.760
Why play dumb?

36:42.230 --> 36:43.630
What do you mean by steal?

36:43.880 --> 36:45.510
That day at the Pill-Tasting Conference,

36:45.510 --> 36:46.000
you

36:46.230 --> 36:46.840
and you—

36:48.960 --> 36:49.590
all of you

36:49.590 --> 36:51.250
saw that I had the jade tablet.

36:51.630 --> 36:52.960
Just because I lost my tablet,

36:52.960 --> 36:54.090
I don't get the pill?

36:55.100 --> 36:56.500
Miss Lyu's heart disease

36:56.840 --> 36:57.960
can be cured

36:58.190 --> 36:59.440
even without the Immortality Pill.

36:59.440 --> 37:00.000
How would I know

37:00.000 --> 37:01.200
if you're lying to me?

37:01.760 --> 37:03.360
Full of hypocrisy.

37:03.650 --> 37:04.750
I don't think you want
the Immortality Pill

37:04.750 --> 37:05.790
for Miss Lyu,

37:05.880 --> 37:07.070
but for yourself.

37:08.670 --> 37:09.110
So...

37:09.130 --> 37:10.780
So what if it's for myself?

37:11.510 --> 37:13.150
Lyu Yunsu is just a mute girl.

37:13.170 --> 37:14.700
How am I worse off than her?

37:21.190 --> 37:23.120
I, Li Si, have outstanding talent.

37:23.670 --> 37:24.880
I practiced sword at 7,

37:24.880 --> 37:27.440
and reached Great Completion in swordplay
at 16.

37:27.440 --> 37:28.150
Even when facing

37:28.150 --> 37:29.550
Foundation Establishment Stage
cultivators,

37:29.550 --> 37:30.960
I was not weak at all.

37:31.710 --> 37:33.770
If you give me another hundred years,

37:33.840 --> 37:35.190
I will be able to compete

37:35.190 --> 37:36.320
with Golden Core cultivators.

37:36.320 --> 37:38.250
Give me another two hundred years,

37:38.280 --> 37:39.960
and I will be able to suppress

37:40.360 --> 37:41.960
Soul Projection stage cultivators
with a mortal's sword,

37:41.960 --> 37:43.320
leaving them completely defenseless.

37:43.320 --> 37:45.090
Give me another five hundred years,

37:45.090 --> 37:46.760
and I will enter sainthood
through the way of the sword,

37:46.760 --> 37:47.960
becoming the first

37:47.960 --> 37:51.290
mortal immortal in the world
to ascend with a physical body!

37:55.920 --> 37:58.190
With my talent,

37:59.150 --> 38:00.110
don't I deserve

38:00.110 --> 38:01.630
an Immortality Pill?

38:02.640 --> 38:03.240
So

38:03.920 --> 38:04.800
your plan started from

38:04.800 --> 38:06.000
when you met Miss Lyu.

38:06.800 --> 38:07.440
You are not

38:07.440 --> 38:08.960
General Lyu's subordinate at all.

38:08.960 --> 38:10.590
Escorting General Lyu's orphan
into the valley

38:10.590 --> 38:12.050
was just an excuse for you.

38:13.190 --> 38:15.190
It was all for the Immortality Pill.

38:15.320 --> 38:16.230
Along the way,

38:16.600 --> 38:17.560
how many people

38:17.590 --> 38:19.710
have you tricked into risking their lives?

38:19.710 --> 38:21.920
Even if I did use Lyu Yunsu,

38:23.080 --> 38:24.210
if it weren't for me,

38:24.280 --> 38:25.760
she would have died
among the refugees long ago.

38:25.760 --> 38:27.360
Would she still be alive now?

38:28.510 --> 38:29.640
I just didn't expect

38:29.960 --> 38:31.490
that your Chongling Valley

38:32.070 --> 38:34.400
would collude with those immortal sects,

38:34.760 --> 38:35.950
allowing them in the valley

38:35.950 --> 38:36.990
to steal and rob,

38:37.590 --> 38:39.520
and steal my Gongshan Jade Tablet.

38:39.960 --> 38:40.480
You...

38:40.550 --> 38:42.280
Don't make false accusations!

38:42.550 --> 38:43.230
Whatever.

38:43.920 --> 38:45.590
Now that I've been caught by you,

38:45.590 --> 38:47.000
it is my fate.

38:47.760 --> 38:49.400
I have nothing to say.

38:50.440 --> 38:51.670
Su Taiyi!

38:52.280 --> 38:54.120
You shameless old thief!

38:54.360 --> 38:55.590
You will die a horrible death!

38:55.590 --> 38:57.000
I'll kill you!

39:07.590 --> 39:09.110
The alchemy furnace is not yet ready.

39:09.110 --> 39:10.630
He who hurts the divine doctor

39:10.630 --> 39:11.690
must not be spared.

39:28.280 --> 39:29.070
Miss Lyu.

39:29.280 --> 39:29.840
Miss Lyu.

39:30.320 --> 39:31.070
Miss Lyu!

39:41.230 --> 39:42.000
Miss Lyu.

40:24.080 --> 40:26.710
[Chongling Valley]

40:38.480 --> 40:39.000
Who's there?
